description: The "Tezos living things(TLT)" is a collection of 5000 generative live videos based on Conway's game of life, you can use start, stop and change the population rules by clicking on each section and using arrow keys.Each 1/1 edition has a unique initiate rule and a unique selection of colors and all of these actions are taken without human touch! This is a living generation of NFTs on the Tezos blockchain!
